data.description: GREAT house on OVERSIZED PRIVATE LOT!!! POSSIBILITIES are endless with the LARGE detached garage with HUGE stand up attic space, potential is INCREDIBLE! This spacious home offers 1584 sqft. Dining room is nicely situated off the living room and kitchen with bay/bow window, decorative chair rail. LIVING room offers WOOD BURNING fireplace w/mantel,carpet. Eat in kitchen, has laminate floors, gas stove, crown molding and wainscott w/direct access to backyard. French doors lead to  Florida/Sun room that offers great additional space with a slider to yard! Master suite has full bath w/shower stall w/ceramic tile from floor to ceiling. Additional full bath w/DECORATIVE vanity, tub w/tile. The two other bedrooms are all nice size. Full laundry room w/extra cabinets for storage. Backyard is PRIVATE, OVERSIZED and has inground pool, sprinklers and a  deck located directly off kitchen, grill has gas hook up. Walk to community park and playground. This is one not to be missed, call today for your showing!!
